{"tid":1657862,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[連登民調] 聽日夜晚 睇民記好定林奠好呀？","createTime":"2019-10-16T09:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T16:11:58.000Z","uid":19513,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"52f7c7658052d3e114d7f732dfb8016e73c76ee8","tid":1657862,"uid":19513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YXkiseW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYXkiseW.jpg&h=a95a040d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各大傳媒機構、採訪主任、編輯及記者：<br />\n<br />\n第二十次民間記者會通知<br />\n<br />\n是次記者會主題為：「居高不仁 還政於民」。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥發表最新施政報告，惟當中施政重點仍未回應市民訴求，更無助解決社會的深層次問題。<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會邀請了多位來自不同界別的團體及專業人士，就個別範疇回應施政報告，並提出切合民間需求的政策建議。屆時民間記者會發言人及嘉賓將以中英發言，之後將設有記者問答環節。<br />\n<br />\n現誠邀    貴機構派員出席採訪，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年10月17日（星期四）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">時間：晚上7:30</span><br />\n<br />\n記者會後將設有問答環節，有興趣進場採訪的媒體請於 10月17日（星期四）早上11:00或之前，以電話（94377274）或電郵 (kim@citizenspc.org) 覆示，以便安排。<br />\n<br />\n如有查詢，請聯絡金先生 （電話：94377274）。謝謝<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n採訪主任、編輯及記者<br />\n<br />\n金先生    謹啟<br />\n2019 年 10月 16日<br />\n<br />\n同日加映林鄭facebook話開live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正皮支持民記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負皮大家都知比邊個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802b3cd16f6d5fcb1c7ae4ba5bd9247a6afc10fe","tid":1657862,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"11f80d6e010745e206df7e1bc4377919e9ba67c8","tid":1657862,"uid":8562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:37:29.000Z","msg":"支持民記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"